{"tid":349543,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[求急救]冷氣機滴水入屋","createTime":"2017-08-06T15:15:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-07T18:26:27.000Z","uid":75529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9e08fd4f1855e6c71653b81a2fc28ed02f439004","tid":349543,"uid":75529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T15:15:02.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n今日開冷氣發現滴到自己啲野濕晒<br />\n於是自己研究左陣<br />\n見到機底好多地方都漏水滲水出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔係好識搞<br />\n所以影底左放上黎請教下應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/230920_3c0b1448fd08e0306586a64b58840b20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F230920_3c0b1448fd08e0306586a64b58840b20.jpg&h=82f1dbab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n啲水由箭咀滲出黎然後直落 btw條m巾係用黎索水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/06/231119_0283b901d15e2b9e9fe08c528bde0772.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F06%2F231119_0283b901d15e2b9e9fe08c528bde0772.jpg&h=a9aef6da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsorry 唔識點focus去後面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n下面個渠位(唔知係咪)啲水好似無郁到 好似係coil啲水都會滴去條渠 正常係去到水？<br />\n<br />\n唔開冷氣真係訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無ching教我點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\